      - M `src/client/shared/Spaarke.Compose.Components/src/widgets/ComposeEditor.tsx` (events subpath)
      - M `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/src/components/shell/ThreePaneShell.tsx` (context hoisted; re-exports)
